This paper deals with word embeddings, which are commonly used in natural language processing (NLP) tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as dictionary learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the improvement of word embeddings in word analogy tasks, which is a common topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves visualization techniques, which can be related to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
